With an ergonomic design that conforms to the contours of your neck, this advanced support ensures optimal alignment of the cervical spine during sleep. Realigning the cervical spine prevents the narrowing of the throat, allowing air to pass easily and preventing throat vibrations and breathing problems. By keeping the neck in its natural position, the airway remains open. This prevents throat vibrations and breathing issues. Get your good night's sl
